{"tid":803743,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅攝多圖少字] 去大阪、奈良、京都影咗啲相","createTime":"2018-09-02T13:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T13:29:06.000Z","uid":38569,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36bf666dd2cf2abd2911d520651a8b35f8e7d4b1","tid":803743,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/221810_4ff32448c06536099ad3cffc68be69ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F221810_4ff32448c06536099ad3cffc68be69ec.jpg&h=df345c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">八月中去咗大阪 其實啱啱返咗兩個星期工就請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一早book咗嘅Grad Trip所以就照去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次因為一班人所以影咗唔算多相 同埋都主要去大景點<br />\n如果睇厭嘅可以當睇吓相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋寫文麻麻都係慳返啲力嚟放相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便放吓舊Post link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/753142/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/753142/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/712781/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/712781/page/1</a><br />\n再舊嘅post已經死哂圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/223400_32c9a60ea6b05531292ee1dc5ba44160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F223400_32c9a60ea6b05531292ee1dc5ba44160.jpg&h=39825427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾意啲相都歡迎Follow我IG睇吓相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tay.wong_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftay.wong_%2F&d=Vy0TySViDNS4XTsTqoj6lpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fc568c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tay.wong_/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/222027_1df17bc6ae255c9995db7931a9308909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F222027_1df17bc6ae255c9995db7931a9308909.jpg&h=2e858f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/222032_0cd20565f4d72482b6e7b6556fef622c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F222032_0cd20565f4d72482b6e7b6556fef622c.jpg&h=3052a058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次嚟到大阪 一嚟就咁嘅天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">京都</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>嵐山</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/224034_344ddd62e0406feaa3681302387df038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F224034_344ddd62e0406feaa3681302387df038.jpg&h=0c1b3416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/224034_11decc347c8be0cee4f0265b69e7e26c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F224034_11decc347c8be0cee4f0265b69e7e26c.jpg&h=942f2321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>五山送火</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/224102_e226139751410dd73bcbe341ed183f99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F224102_e226139751410dd73bcbe341ed183f99.jpg&h=0aaea723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/224102_022bf78b177ef577ed74b78de21be535.jpg\" dat